  "detailed_description": "Take control of the train which will become your haven on the rails. Collect resources, craft equipment, construct a cozy house on railway cars, and travel through the carefully handcrafted locations to explore the story of a zombie apocalypse world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><strong>Take control of the train</strong> which will become your haven on the rails. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/f8da62259ed3c2897b8bec44f0b3ae8a.poster.avif?t=1771504324\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/f8da62259ed3c2897b8bec44f0b3ae8a.webm?t=1771504324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/f8da62259ed3c2897b8bec44f0b3ae8a.mp4?t=1771504324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explore the story</strong> by traveling through the extensive and carefully handcrafted locations where each of which will require you to overcome some specific challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/8d0e4e6aee914b6fb0b6e91e6c711c2b.poster.avif?t=1771504324\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/8d0e4e6aee914b6fb0b6e91e6c711c2b.webm?t=1771504324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/8d0e4e6aee914b6fb0b6e91e6c711c2b.mp4?t=1771504324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Find a robotic companion.</strong> Equip your robot with combat and support equipment to make your adventures easier.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/209877deab5608a7350b02fce69f1cb9.poster.avif?t=1771504324\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/209877deab5608a7350b02fce69f1cb9.webm?t=1771504324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/209877deab5608a7350b02fce69f1cb9.mp4?t=1771504324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Construct a home on railway cars.</strong> Various workbenches, storage containers, dozens of decoration elements, and the possibility to place any inventory item on any surface, will allow you to unleash your creativity and build a cozy mobile house that will keep you safe from the dangers of the outer world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/43fce0e4bd791e4957f1daad40201fb5.poster.avif?t=1771504324\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/43fce0e4bd791e4957f1daad40201fb5.webm?t=1771504324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/43fce0e4bd791e4957f1daad40201fb5.mp4?t=1771504324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/4edb330bdf8c9e765b0d1b1f871b59b5.poster.avif?t=1771504324\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/4edb330bdf8c9e765b0d1b1f871b59b5.webm?t=1771504324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/4edb330bdf8c9e765b0d1b1f871b59b5.mp4?t=1771504324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Fight against a horde of various zombies.</strong> Each type of zombie has its own behavior, tactics, strengths, and weakness. Loot and craft different weapons to improve your survival capabilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/98a92faa98cb867712dcaba532e0e01a.poster.avif?t=1771504324\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/98a92faa98cb867712dcaba532e0e01a.webm?t=1771504324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1262460/extras/98a92faa98cb867712dcaba532e0e01a.mp4?t=1771504324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
